<p>South Kearney neighborhoods near the University of Nebraska at Kearney campus feature a mix of older and newer construction. Many homes in this area have mature trees that may impact solar panel placement, requiring careful site assessment. The Yanney Park area offers premium locations with large roofs suitable for substantial solar arrays. North Kearney's residential areas typically feature ranch-style homes ideal for ground-mount solar systems when roof conditions aren't optimal.</p>

